---
import Body from '../layouts/Body.astro';
import image from '../assets/images/introduction.png';
---

<Body>
  <div>
    <h3>Instant group Chats</h3>
    <p>
      Introducing ChatApp V2: The Next Generation of Chatting ChatApp V2 is the
      upgraded version of KSChat, a chat application that offers a variety of
      features for users to enjoy. With ChatApp V2, users can easily create an
      account, log in and out, view their own and other users profiles.
    </p>
    <img src={image} alt='ChatApp Demo' />
  </div>
</Body>

<style>
  div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 50px 20px 50px;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--colorPrimary);
    font-family: var(--fontPrimary);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--colorTertiary);
    font-family: var(--fontSecondary);
    max-width: 625px;
    padding: 25px 0 50px 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  img {
    max-width: 990px;
  }

  img::after {
  }
</style>
